Recommends: gnome-screenshot
Description: Smart OCR tool for GNOME desktop with image preprocessing
 GNOME Text Extractor is an intelligent OCR (Optical Character Recognition)
 tool that extracts text from screenshots with automatic image preprocessing.
 .
 Features:
  * Smart image preprocessing with automatic dark mode detection
  * Fast and accurate text extraction using RapidOCR with ONNX runtime
  * Seamless GNOME desktop integration
  * Automatic clipboard support
  * Desktop notifications for extraction status
  * Support for multiple screenshot tools
 .
 The tool automatically detects and inverts dark-mode screenshots for
 better OCR accuracy, making it ideal for developers and users who
 frequently need to extract text from screenshots.
